202486.「マジカル★カーニバルは ４対４の\n パーティバトル限定カボ。\n<br>\n:
Magical Carnival is a 4-on-4 party battle only kabob, a fun festival where players collect carnival points by smashing sweets against
each other for 3 minutes! If you defeat your opponent during the carnival, 30 points will be added to your carnival points. On the other
hand, if you are defeated, you lose 20 percent of your carnival points, move to the resurrection point, and then return to the
carnival. The party with the higher total points at the end of the time limit wins. At the end of the carnival, you will receive a
Halloween stamp for each win! If you win, you get 20 stamps, if you tie, you get 15 stamps, and if you lose, you get only 10 stamps. You
will also receive an additional stamp for each opponent you defeat. Everyone must work together to win! As a special rule, you must
enter the game alone. You can't enter with a party, so please be careful. The beauty of a carnival is that you can enjoy the festivities
with people you don't know! I hope you will take this opportunity to enjoy it. Also, chatting is not allowed. Don't worry. Even if
we don't exchange words, we can create a sense of unity. That's all for now... I'm looking forward to seeing you at the Magical Carnival!

202487.「今回の特別ルールとして カーニバル中の\n 職業は オバケ あくま ミイラ男:
As a special rule, the locations during the carnival are limited to ghost Demon Mummy Boy Jack. These locations cannot be used as items.
Skills and parameter increase effects acquired by other vocation's unique skills will not work either. Shoko Raa Tack can attack
opponents in a straight line. Shoko Raa Tack is a kabob that allows you to attack an opponent in a straight line. Shoko La Cross is
a kabo that can attack opponents in front of, behind, left and right of you. Kyan Didrop is a kabo that attacks opponents around you. The
Jamu Bomber and Butter Bomber can drop a Bakudan on your opponent's feet. If you are dropped, run away as fast as you can! Everyone
will be fighting with the same parameters and skills, so enjoy a different kind of battle!

202488.「マジカル★カーニバルが始まると 画面上部に\n 残り時間と パーティの合計ポイ:
When Magical Carnival starts, the time remaining and the party's total points are displayed at the top of the screen... and the
carnival points of each player are displayed at the top left of the screen. The icon above each player's head indicates the amount of
carnival points. The more prominent the icon, the more points you have.

202489.「フレンドや 同じチームのメンバーが\n マジカル★カーニバルに 参加すると\n:
